Ok, this does work, I have played it, here is what you have to do.....
First download daemon tools if you havnt got the program, here is the link http://www.daemon-tools.cc/dtcc/download.php?mode=Download&id=34
Then you right click the daemon tools icon at the bottom of your screen, and go to virtual CD/DVD, set number of divices, and click 2 divices.
Then, you left click again, go to virtual DVD, go to one drive, and click mount image. 
Then, you browse and mount file SWAT 4 _ 1.
You then go to my computer, double click the drive where swat 4 is mounted, and install the program.
During the installation, it asks, "insert CD 2", you repeat the mounting thing for the file SWAT 4_ 2, in the other drive, and press ok.
After you have installed it, you have to put in the crack, so you copy the SWAT 4 icon, and paste it  in the folder where you installed swat 4. It will ask to replace an icon, you press yes. And thats it.....shortcuts should work
